ZH: 这座城市周围起伏的山峦形成了一道壮丽的天然屏障。
EN: The undulating mountains surrounding this city create a magnificent natural barrier.

ZH: 我爱沿着山峦蜿蜒的小路散步。
EN: I love taking walks along the winding paths through the mountains.

ZH: 这座城市的风景优美，有壮丽的山峦和清澈的湖泊。
EN: This city has beautiful scenery with majestic mountains and clear lakes.

ZH: 沿着山峦上的小径，我们终于到达了目的地。
EN: Following the path on the mountain range, we finally reached our destination.

ZH: 山峦的轮廓在晨光中显得格外婀娜多姿。
EN: The contour of the mountain range appears particularly graceful and beautiful in the morning light.

ZH: 从山顶上望去，可以看到连绵起伏的山峦一直延伸到远方。
EN: From the mountaintop, you can see the undulating mountain range extending into the distance.

ZH: 在这片山峦上，有许多隐居者选择过一种宁静的生活。
EN: Many hermits have chosen a peaceful life in this mountain range.

ZH: 这片山峦是野生动植物世界中的天然乐园。
EN: This mountain range is a natural paradise for wildlife and plants.

ZH: 山峦之间流淌着清澈的溪水，给人一种宁静和宜人的感觉。
EN: Clear streams flow between the mountain ranges, giving a sense of tranquility and pleasantness.

ZH: 山峦之间有着许多美丽的瀑布，形成了壮观的风景。
EN: There are many beautiful waterfalls between the mountain ranges, creating a spectacular view.

ZH: 我喜欢徒步穿越这片峻峭的山峦，感受大自然的力量和美丽。
EN: I enjoy hiking through these steep mountain ranges, experiencing the power and beauty of nature.

ZH: 气势磅礴的山峦向我们展示了大自然的壮丽和伟大。
EN: The majestic mountain ranges showcase the magnificence and grandeur of nature to us.

ZH: 我在山峦上找到了一片宁静的角落，远离了喧嚣的城市生活。
EN: I found a peaceful corner on the mountain range, far away from the hustle and bustle of city life.

ZH: 蜿蜒而上的山峦道路使人们可以欣赏到不同高度的美景。
EN: The winding mountain roads allow people to appreciate the beautiful views at different altitudes.

ZH: 在阳光的照射下，山峦的轮廓更加清晰可见。
EN: Under the sunlight, the contours of the mountain range are even more distinct.

ZH: 琳琅满目的颜色在山峦上交织成绚丽的景象。
EN: An array of colors interweave into a splendid scene on the mountain range.

ZH: 这座城市依山傍水，被壮丽的山峦环绕着。
EN: This city is nestled beside the mountains and surrounded by majestic mountain ranges.

ZH: 在这片山峦之中，有一座古老的寺庙守护着这片土地。
EN: Within this mountain range, there is an ancient temple guarding this land.

ZH: 我梦想着能够攀登这座雄伟的山峦，征服自己的内心恐惧。
EN: I dream of being able to climb this majestic mountain range and conquer my inner fears.
